description:
In case you missed it, a video of Elephants at the San Diego zoo during an earthquake went viral, in which they formed an “alert circle” to protect the young. It was a cute video, but not something you would think would be living rent-free in a politician's mind, especially the one who almost became the Leader of the Free World. But that is exactly the case, as Kamala claims the Dems need to be more like elephants.


Kamala's dumb elephant story elucidates one key fact: leftists are collectivists, conservatives are individualists. pic.twitter.com/EdMqpe6LQ2
— Libby Emmons (@libbyemmons) May 1, 2025
title: Kamala Harris returns for anti-Trump speech, instead claims elephants live rent-free in her head (at least something does)
